Class Description
Company
Company is a class that holds Customer's, Employee's, Delivery's and also implements Locatable interface.
CompanyTester  
Customer
Customer is a subclass of Person class which can hold and send an item.
Delivery
Delivery is an abstract class which carries properties for package no and Customers for receiver and sender.
Employee
Employee class is a subclass of Person class which implements following properties: salary, delivery, employee no.
Item
Item is a class that accepts weight and content values.
Locatable
Locatable interface is inherited by classes which implement positions.
Mail
Mail is a subclass of Delivery class, which implements a String type of content.
Package
Package is a subclass of Delivery class, which implements an Item type of content.
Person
Person is an abstract class that has methods for objects with names and locations.
